ghlighted however for\ninsulating dielectric substrate applications, microwave CVD may destroy these\ndesirable properties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Jun 2019 16:48:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Nov 2019 11:16:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-12"}
