\\mathring{\\mathcal P}_{r+k+1}^-\\Lambda^{n-k}$ and between $\\mathcal\nP_r^-\\Lambda^k$ and $\\mathring{\\mathcal P}_{r+k}\\Lambda^{n-k}$, which we\nillustrate with examples.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Jun 2019 18:14:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 23 Jan 2021 19:55:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-15"}
