rned by the imitation process, which leads to an\nintermediate average value of the preferred project scales and an intermediate\nlevel of cooperation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 15 Jun 2019 13:22:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 21 Nov 2019 08:38:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-19"}
